1. Juče sam *prodao* svoj stari telefon. (Yesterday, I *sold* my old phone.)
2. On je odlučio da *proda* svoj stan. (He decided to *sell* his apartment.)
3. Kada budeš spreman, *prodaću* ti moju gitaru. (When you're ready, I'll *sell* you my guitar.)
4. Ona neće *prodati* svoju kolekciju knjiga. (She won't *sell* her book collection.)
5. Hoću da *prodajem* svoje proizvode online. (I want to *sell* my products online.)
6. Kad sam bila na pijaci, *prodavačica* mi je dala popust. (When I was at the market, the *saleswoman* gave me a discount.)
7. Bio je srećan kad je *prodao* svoju umetničku sliku. (He was happy when he *sold* his art painting.)
8. Oni planiraju da *prodaju* kuću i kupe veću. (They plan to *sell* their house and buy a bigger one.)
9. *Prodavač* mi je rekao da je proizvod na akciji. (The *seller* told me that the product was on sale.)
10. Moram *prodati* svoj auto jer mi treba novac. (I have to *sell* my car because I need money.)